<% String title = "FAQ"; %>
<%@ include file="layouts/header.jsp"%>
<div class="container text-center mt-5 mb-2">
    <h1 class="mb-0">FREQUENTLY ASKED QUESTIONS</h1>
</div>
<div class="container text-center mt-5 mb-2">
    <h1 class="mb-0">How do I create an account?</h1>
    <p>Visit our login page and select "Create an account" and proceed to enter your account information.</p>
    <p>Once completed, enter submit and proceed to the login page and enter the appropriate information.</p>
</div>
<div class="container text-center mt-5 mb-2">
    <h1 class="mb-0">How do I select a store to shop at?</h1>
    <p>To find a store to shop at, you can visit either the suggested sotre list and choose your desired store.</p>
    <p>You can also visit our store list which in found on our homepage to view all available stores using our service.</p>
</div>
<div class="container text-center mt-5 mb-2">
    <h1 class="mb-0">How do I add items into my cart?</h1>
    <p>To add items into the cart, select a store you wish to shop from. Then select an item you wish to add to your cart and click "Add To Cart".</p>
</div>
<div class="container text-center mt-5 mb-2">
    <h1 class="mb-0">How do I remove items from my cart?</h1>
    <p>To remove an item from your cart, select cart located in the top header. Proceed to click "Remove" to remove item from cart.</p>
</div>
